Name: Skinny Crunch Peanut Butter (10 packs of 5 bars)
Description: Nutty about, well… nuts? We have the perfect indulgent treat for you. Go nuts for our peanut butter crunch bar, that’s less than 75 calories! Enjoy the buttery, sweet and ever so slightly salty flavour combos of this nutty and crunchy cereal bar – all dipped and drizzled in a light layer of milk choc for extra scrumminess, and full of fibre too!

Name: Skinny Dream Choc Peanut Bar (10 packs of 5 bars)
Description: Say hello to our peanut flavoured Skinny Dream, totting up only 96 calories per bar! This nutty flavoured nougat snack bar is not only lathered in tasty milk chocolate and crunchy nut pieces, but also has an extra layer of cheeky caramel on top. Talk about the snack of our dreams!

Name: Skinny Dream Rocky Road (10 packs of 5 bars)
Description: Just when you thought we couldn’t get any dreamier… meet our Skinny Dream Rocky Road. Devoted dessert lovers can bite into a soft cereal bar loaded with gooey marshmallows, sweet raspberries, crunchy honeycomb pieces, and all topped off with a scrummy layer of silky milk chocolate drizzle. Oh, and did we mention you get all of this for less than 75 calories?!

Name: Skinny Dream Salted Caramel (10 packs of 5 bars)
Description: Salted Caramel flavoured Skinny Dream, coming in at a fabulous 99 calories! This caramel flavoured nougat snack bar is not only covered in chocolate and tasty cereal pieces, but also has a silky layer of salted caramel on top. You’ll need to taste it to believe it!

Name: Skinny Whip Double Chocolate
Description: Chocolate flavoured nougat bars coated in milk chocolate

Name: Skinny Whip Latte & Chocolate (10 Packs)
Description: (25g per bar)\n\nFinally you coffee lovers can rejoice! We’ve made a scrummy Skinny Bar that’s crammed with the creamy taste of a silky latte, as well as being full of fluffy nougat and encased in a luxurious layer of milk choc. Now that’s what we call a morning pick me up! And yep, as always we’re keeping things under 99 calories.

Name: Skinny Chocolate Crunch Fruit & Nut (10 packs of 5 bars)
Description: Need an extra indulgent crunch in your life? Then look no further. This indulgently crispy chocolate covered snack bar is packed with raisins and peanuts, then wrapped up in milk chocolate. And all of this for less than 99 calories!

Name: Skinny Chocolate Crunch Honeycomb (10 packs of 5 bars)
Description: Need an extra indulgent crunch in your life? Then look no further. This indulgently crispy chocolate covered snack bar is packed with honeycomb.  The perfect sweet treat to satisfy all your cravings and less than 99 calories per bar.

Description:
More indulgence, but still no more than 99 cals…

\n

Looking for even more crunch for your munch? It’s time to bite into our sweetest crunch bar yet. Enjoy this crispy chocolatey snack bar, packed with sweet freeze-dried raspberries and crispy cereal pieces – lovingly dipped in a layer of tempting dark chocolate. And you can have all of this scrumptiousness for less than 99 calories!

Name: Skinny Crunch Mint & Dark Chocolate (10 packs of 5 bars)
Description: Introducing our marvelous mint and dark chocolate Skinny Crunch! Chomp your way through this minty crispy cereal bar, drizzled in luxurious dark chocolate. Less than 75 Calories per bar.

Name: Skinny Crunch Chocolate Orange (10 packs of 5 bars)
Description: If you’re crazy about chocolate orange then look no further! Packed with fibre and a totting up to less than 75 calories, it’s time to chomp your way through this deliciously indulgent chocolate orange cereal bar, drizzled and dipped in cheeky layers of milk chocolate. Not bad for a low-calorie snack…

Name: Skinny Crunch Sticky Toffee (10 packs of 5 bars)
Description: As far as low-calorie snacks go, this one is pretty special. Tuck into this sticky toffee flavoured cereal bar – loaded with cheeky little pieces of real sticky toffee and drizzled in a layer of lush milk chocolate. Just one nibble and you’ll be in buttery, sweet toffee heaven, and all for less than 75 calories!

Name: Skinny Dream Choc Toffee Bar (10 packs of 5 bars)
Description: We hear this may be one of our most delicious treats so far! Introducing our toffee flavoured Skinny Dream, coming in at a fabulous 93 calories! This toffee flavoured nougat snack bar is not only covered in chocolate and tasty cereal pieces, but also layered with a silky layer of sweet caramel on top. You’ll need to taste it to believe it!

Description: Countdown to Christmas with these deliciously indulgent low-calorie treats. 24 doors with 8 different Skinny Bars.
